<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan>
<expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> bey Reyn,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> in Peyern und grafen zu Mortani
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat <expan>Engelh<ex>art</ex></expan>
                        Marschalk von Tonrsperg, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>newlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> brief gesandt und <add>darinn</add> abgesagt
                        von sprüch <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die
                            <expan>F<ex>ridrich</ex></expan> Zesel, der doch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gesworn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ist, zu uns hab, dar<add>an uns von dem Zesel
                            ungütlich beschiht. Dar</add>auf <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                            <add>dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Marschalk</add>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> und <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>,
                        wie <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> sache gestalt sein, des uns kein
                        antwurt von im <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, <add>daz wir niht
                                    <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, ob wir und die
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vor im sicher sein</add>. Darumb
                        wir <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Wynmar, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>furstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu reden. Und <pb facs="#facs_249" id="123v"/>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                        fleiss, was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in den <expan>vorg<ex>eschriben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        gnade <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir in darinn
                                <expan>gnedigkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> verhörn, im des
                                <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und günstklich
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> von ew <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wellet. Als etc. Das wellen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> d<ex>omi</ex>nicam
                            <expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
